<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>3 Card Blog Layout</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100">

  <!-- Navbar -->
  <%- include("../partials/navbar") %>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-purple-700 mb-10">Latest Blog Posts</h1>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#993BFB] mb-1">The Power of Simplicity</h2>
        <h3 class="text-md font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2">Why Less is Often More</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Minimalism in design helps users focus on what matters most. Learn how to simplify your UI for better results.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#993BFB] mb-1">Understanding Async JS</h2>
        <h3 class="text-md font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2">Promises, Async/Await</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">JavaScript asynchronous behavior can be confusing. This post explains how to handle async code effectively.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#993BFB] mb-1">SEO for Beginners</h2>
        <h3 class="text-md font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2">Rank Higher on Google</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Learn the basics of search engine optimization and how to structure content to increase visibility.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
